{"tid":1674280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚已預習25/10重慶大廈感謝日！探子實地探測分享+嚐鮮報告","createTime":"2019-10-25T06:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T01:01:38.000Z","uid":284485,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f510379a5e5248496f6fa259a30e15c73ec186b0","tid":1674280,"uid":284485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:33:59.000Z","msg":"話說之前南亞手足上星期同香港人成功CONNECT，毛漢叔更加大大發聲講咗我哋好多嘅心底話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我一見到有CK感謝日，即刻就決定要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>(25/10)重慶大廈感謝日(UST南亞仔之微願）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過我老婆今晚唔得，所以約咗尋<br />\n晚去，都好嘅，唔駛咁多人，同埋可以率先睇驗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多住，去相先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JCjHv0s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJCjHv0s.jpg&h=9f20bb6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dHzwpku.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdHzwpku.jpg&h=f2eadddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到咁多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就知好食啦<br />\n呢味係雞，個咖喱真係真心堅超級好食！！薄餅都係超激賞<br />\n本來喉嚨痛諗住唔order,但係我哋覺得一場嚟到唔食名菜好嗮料，最後都係嗌咗<br />\n食落就會發覺，平日食嘅假咖喱真係好流，呢個真 &bull; 咖喱個味好rich好濃郁係堅正<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gF4oZUW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgF4oZUW.jpg&h=bcd558a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我喺CK門口仲有啲十五十六唔知好唔好入去（我真係未入過去重慶）,好彩我老婆夠醒，已經一早睇定有邊幾間好食，同埋都見有香港人行入去，卒之成功入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實都係喺新X期FB有個post專講CK，所以我哋去嗰間嘢嗰陣都有好多香港人一齊去到C座等𨋢，一入到間餐廳裡面，全部都係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMenu有曬中文字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有埋數目字篤住嚟order好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，啲侍應仲識啲廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等到有位坐，嗌完嘢食之後，望下出面，已經有成廿幾人排緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於實在太多人，等咗一陣都係淨係個沙律嚟咗，於是追一追侍應order<br />\n嗰個印度小姐睇嚟應該係老闆嘅千金，我雖然本身唔係太鍾意鄭欣宜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但係佢好nice好友善，講嘅英文（美式口音）同廣東話都好流利<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢係度同我哋講sorry，佢話佢哋冇預計過有咁多人，會盡量加快出菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢話本來唔知點解咁多人，係問過其他同事先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實未到正日，都已經幾多人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日應該都多人<br />\n好在CK都好多食肆，一間多人都可以去第二間 <br />\n或者喺地下嗰層買，有好多小食或者外賣，目測似乎都係唔錯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都可以逛下地下嗰層，幾有feel幾值得睇下<br />\n不過提提大家注意安全，有啲地方可能會品流複雜，譬如賓館嘅層數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（地下等𨋢，會見到水牌寫住邊層係餐廳邊層係賓館）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將來如果多啲人體驗過CK呢個地方冇咁抗拒<br />\n同埋以食物嘅水準嚟睇<br />\n將會keep住有香港巴絲繼續嚟幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望食物質素唔會因為人多而下降啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋香港都有啲食肆，因為經FB嘅post（新X期等等）draw咗好多人嚟食<br />\n令到個老闆以為嚟緊會keep住多客而洗好多錢，大肆擴充<br />\n點知熱潮一過啲人就唔再嚟，令到老闆中曬伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望唔會出現喺重慶佢哋身上<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>最後想講，我見到香港同南亞connect係好開心，就算種族唔同，只要佢哋認同香港人嘅核心價值，都係香港人，希望大家努力，加油！<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀（多圖）：<br />\n10/25 食爆重慶日實用指南出爐喇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1673727\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1673727</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc3ffe052f68086b18a52f9ce4686610c73b2420","tid":1674280,"uid":28105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:35:32.000Z","msg":"【 香 港 人 物 資  】 多 元 化 物 資 站 ， 前 線 手 足 需 要 我 地 既 幫 忙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1673354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1673354</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"77011741598680a3a82f8e2ee3c32c434d8f1c89","tid":1674280,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:35:44.000Z","msg":"提大家今個星期六日有咩活動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>星期六 10 &middot; 26 醫護抗暴 - 醫療專職集會</strong></span><br />\n- 18:00 遮打花園 [已獲不反對通知書]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>星期日 10 &middot; 27 <br />\n追究警暴 守護民眾記者 守護穆斯林</strong></span><br />\n- 15:00 尖沙咀梳士巴利道公園<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>星期日 10 &middot; 27 自由之鶴追悼會</strong></span><br />\n- 16:00 - 20:00 觀塘海濱公園"},{"pid":"f435dbe5d5161fce2c27bc04f2fe29ad25d1c36b","tid":1674280,"uid":284485,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:35:57.000Z","msg":"PS<br />\n咖喱其實係幾辣，但係因為好食，你會一路覺得辣，一路又會係咁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩人食相裡面有嘅嘢，埋單要$140<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住之後加單再嗌嘢食，因為要等好耐<br />\n<br />\n我哋都有啲後悔冇嗌多啲嘢食，到最後食唔飽，要返屋企煮個麵保返數<br />\n<br />\n如果驚會好多人，可以去旺角女人街都有幾間印度食肆，或者如去開深水埗嘅話，喺政府合署，嘉頓方向對面有間巴基斯坦薄餅店試下都得（希望第日我都有機會試試）"},{"pid":"606e0d87d59ba74b25ec3c311fbf912da2e31f82","tid":1674280,"uid":254729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e34628f7df58d4ebab35f635fd4a1372a19c609","tid":1674280,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71bc5cdb145f39bc9dbbb5f533e44d0f30a1efb3","tid":1674280,"uid":34518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0344734910cc9b23e914ee5c9e53abb610143fb","tid":1674280,"uid":15053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f435dbe5d5161fce2c27bc04f2fe29ad25d1c36b","tid":1674280,"uid":284485,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:35:57.000Z","msg":"PS<br />\n咖喱其實係幾辣，但係因為好食，你會一路覺得辣，一路又會係咁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩人食相裡面有嘅嘢，埋單要$140<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住之後加單再嗌嘢食，因為要等好耐<br />\n<br />\n我哋都有啲後悔冇嗌多啲嘢食，到最後食唔飽，要返屋企煮個麵保返數<br />\n<br />\n如果驚會好多人，可以去旺角女人街都有幾間印度食肆，或者如去開深水埗嘅話，喺政府合署，嘉頓方向對面有間巴基斯坦薄餅店試下都得（希望第日我都有機會試試）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:48:57.000Z","msg":"深水埗狗署對面有間深水埗咖喱 都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋黨鐵站高登嗰邊個出口附近都有間印度餐廳"},{"pid":"1d50c1ce4b8ae1f8bda0e59a76dfeaee7921c4f2","tid":1674280,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:56:50.000Z","msg":"印度茶真心正"},{"pid":"5e073ab9cfbadaa491497532988ca8e3351d6168","tid":1674280,"uid":284485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0344734910cc9b23e914ee5c9e53abb610143fb","tid":1674280,"uid":15053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f435dbe5d5161fce2c27bc04f2fe29ad25d1c36b","tid":1674280,"uid":284485,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:35:57.000Z","msg":"PS<br />\n咖喱其實係幾辣，但係因為好食，你會一路覺得辣，一路又會係咁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩人食相裡面有嘅嘢，埋單要$140<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住之後加單再嗌嘢食，因為要等好耐<br />\n<br />\n我哋都有啲後悔冇嗌多啲嘢食，到最後食唔飽，要返屋企煮個麵保返數<br />\n<br />\n如果驚會好多人，可以去旺角女人街都有幾間印度食肆，或者如去開深水埗嘅話，喺政府合署，嘉頓方向對面有間巴基斯坦薄餅店試下都得（希望第日我都有機會試試）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:48:57.000Z","msg":"深水埗狗署對面有間深水埗咖喱 都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋黨鐵站高登嗰邊個出口附近都有間印度餐廳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40821f22e8c6ee8aae502ef592f95bb0117f210d","tid":1674280,"uid":284485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":